			<P><B>Main activities</B> 
			</P>
			<UL>
				<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Development of software for
				the&nbsp;radiosounding analysis and the computation of
				instability indices. 
				</P>
				<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Development of ensemble neural
				network tools for short-time thunderstorm and rain forecast,
				using instability indices derived by radiosoundings or GCM. 
				</P>
				<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Conversion in NetCDF and GRIB
				formats of meteo data (stations, soundings, satellite,
				models,...) 
				</P>
				<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Visualization of real time meto
				data using the NCAR &quot;ZEBRA&quot; software. 
				</P>
				<LI><P>Case studies and research on convection, rainfall and
				hail. 
				</P>
